                </td><td>
                <p>We would like to collect information about the workshop you are planning or preparing to move.  Once your workshop has progressed through our workflow, it will be added to the LiveLabs system.<br><br>Please enter the required information initially.  Additional info can be added as you progress through rollout.  If you have any questions about how to fill this out, please watch the <strong>WATCH Submission process video</strong. on the left menu.</p><p>Enter one email per area, do not duplicate emails</p>
                </td></tr></table>
